# Privacy Policy

**My Three Things** does not collect, store, or share any personal or sensitive user data.

## Data Collection

We do not collect or transmit any personal information or analytics. All data (such as your tasks) is stored locally on your device using Android's secure storage mechanisms (DataStore), and is never shared with third parties.

## Third-party Access

The app does not use any third-party services or libraries that collect data.

